    {
      "sender_name": "Gutemberg Batista Lacerda",
      "timestamp_ms": 1753231553493,
      "content": "Gutemberg enviou um anexo.",
      "share": {
        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DMac_a0MdJE/?id=3682383148751114820_52295391595",
        "share_text": "A can\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00a3o D\u00c3\u00a9g\u00c3\u00a9n\u00c3\u00a9rations (Degenera\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00b5es) composta pela banda  Mes A\u00c3\u00afeux (Meus Antepassados) n\u00c3\u00a3o trata somente de terras, ela tamb\u00c3\u00a9m faz uma reflex\u00c3\u00a3o sobre nossa ess\u00c3\u00aancia, nossas ra\u00c3\u00adzes e em como o mundo contempor\u00c3\u00a2neo afeta nossas vidas.\n\nTradu\u00c3\u00a7\u00c3\u00a3o e V\u00c3\u00addeo completo na nossa p\u00c3\u00a1gina Ra\u00c3\u00adzes Geneal\u00c3\u00b3gicas no YouTube. \nLINK NA \u00f0\u009f\u0085\u00b1\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u00ac\u0086\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00f0\u009f\u0085\u00be\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\n\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 Cr\u00c3\u00a9ditos v\u00c3\u00addeo: reland / v\u00c3\u00addeo viral \n\n\u00f0\u009f\u0091\u0087\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00bd\u00f0\u009f\u0091\u0087\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00bd\nSequ\u00c3\u00aancia correta:\nAv\u00c3\u00b4: Pai do seu pai ou m\u00c3\u00a3e.\nBisav\u00c3\u00b4: Pai do seu av\u00c3\u00b4 ou av\u00c3\u00b3.\nTrisav\u00c3\u00b4: Pai do seu bisav\u00c3\u00b4.\nTatarav\u00c3\u00b4: Pai do seu trisav\u00c3\u00b4. Tamb\u00c3\u00a9m chamado de tetrav\u00c3\u00b4, embora \"tatarav\u00c3\u00b4\" seja mais comum na linguagem popular. \n\nGosta de Hist\u00c3\u00b3ria e pesquisas geneal\u00c3\u00b3gicas? Siga o nosso perfil \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\nEnvie para algu\u00c3\u00a9m que gosta desse tema.\u00f0\u009f\u0092\u008c\n.\n.\n.\n#passado #brasil #espa\u00c3\u00b1a #europa #investigaciones #geneal\u00c3\u00b3gicas #genealog\u00c3\u00ada #familia #medieval #brasil #memorias #ra\u00c3\u00adzes #origens #ancestro #libros #c\u00c3\u00adntiarosa #rosacs #arvoregenealogica #escritor #livros #escritoresbrasileiros #escritor #literatura #literaturainfantil #history #historia #medieval",
        "original_content_owner": "raizesgenealogicas_cintiarosa"
      },
